snippet.textDisplay:
I've been homeless most my life and it's usually not to bad if you can find a good place to sleep.. But there's one thing l that will stick with me forever, when I was about 15 I was sleeping near a marina up behind the building so anyway I was asleep for a few hours and at about 3am I woke up with water falling on me at first I just thought it was rain so I tucked my head out of the sleeping bag and saw a guy he would have been about 40 years old and I was really scared until I saw he was pissing on me then I got mad i jumped up and screamed at him while he ran off I went back to my stuff and moved away I obviously didn't want to sleep in the bag now but I had to so I sniffed it to see how bad it was and all I could smell was gas... Yeah this guy was pouring gas on me i don't even want to think what he was going to do next

Sorry about the spelling I didn't really get the chance to go to school
